* Headnode reboot or shutdown *
  1. check /work8 is mounted on head node as well as all compute nodes
  2. check all network and internet connections

* Headnode power failure *
  1. check /work8 is mounted on head node as well as all compute nodes
  2. check all network and internet connections
  3. check quota ```quotacheck -vug /work8```, see https://hpc-um.slack.com/files/U0204V4V5FA/F0239QSG807/quotacheck.sh
  

* Compute nodes reboot or shutdown *
  1. check /scratch1 on all compute nodes to be linked to /state/partition1
  2. check /scratch2 on compute-0-2 to be linked to /state/partition2
